dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Kyle Reed. May I have your name please?
Hello Kyle, my name is Virginia Richardson.
Nice to meet you, Virginia. Can you please provide me with the license plate number of the vehicle involved in the incident?
Sure, it's Alpha Bravo Charlie seven eight nine.
Thank you, Virginia. Could you also confirm the date of the accident in a day, month, year format?
The accident happened on two five zero four two zero two two.
Thank you for providing that information, Virginia. We will review your claim and get back to you shortly.
Is there anything else you would like to add or inquire about today, Virginia?
No, that would be all for now. Thank you, Kyle.
You're welcome, Virginia. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
